=== Install ===
 mkdir -p ~/.vim/plugin
 wget -O ~/.vim/plugin/gnupg.vim http://www.vim.org/scripts/download_script.php?src_id=12200 

=== Transparently Edit Encrypted Files ===
 vim secrets.gpg

